{"tid":1088440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河南人：為什麼在廣東說兒化音，廣東服務員都聽不懂？","createTime":"2019-04-02T05:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T09:54:42.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":241,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"67e6ad0454a14085957aa00550f645d880e05d03","tid":1088440,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5741500578?red_tag=0775348982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5741500578%3Fred_tag%3D0775348982&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m68dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=4c711849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5741500578?red_tag=0775348982</a><br />\n<br />\n我一河南人，雖說普通話沒有標準到像是承德人一樣吧，但說話也沒帶有濃重的胡辣湯味兒啊，在北方去哪兒交流都無障礙的。<br />\n但來到廣東之後，和快遞員什麼的說話，尤其是打電話，<strong><ins>即使我一個字一個字的大聲的說，他們還是會時常&ldquo;啊？你說什麼？&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n在河南確實有一些老人們對普通話不是很敏感，而粵語和以官話為基礎的普通話差的更遠，廣東人會不會有聽不明白普通話的情況？"},{"pid":"02b52ca02b8c4077c53e21605aea7649c1091fcd","tid":1088440,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":42,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"我們寧波一些老人確實是聽不太懂普通話，像我老外婆，看電視完全靠猜，哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收起回复2樓2018-06-11 15:31<br />\n<br />\n李文文1993: 這邊快遞員可都是年輕人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n用詞習慣不同，是會導致這樣的情況的，還有就是兒化音，和一些語調的問題，可能你覺得沒什麼，但是有時候別人是不能理解你的意思的。當然聽不懂普通話基本是不存在的😂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收起回復來自Android客戶端4樓2018-06-11 16:45<br />\n<br />\n李文文1993: 呃 我說話確實兒化音較多"},{"pid":"025d59fe23b78106014d9331d42a8761730249f7","tid":1088440,"uid":36901,"like":247,"dislike":13,"score":234,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"其實全個南方都停不懂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e3525fdde818c99c1356c551440dcee7d30b2a","tid":1088440,"uid":130695,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"支那狗話 乜柒都"},{"pid":"41205fefbe96951a0c15343af604edf8ebcfbdd9","tid":1088440,"uid":227642,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:16:15.000Z","msg":"中國人不嬲都睇唔起非本地戶口嘅人，聽到都當你死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1705760bc7d4d9675c7d28e13e21a0c013e4c70","tid":1088440,"uid":12628,"like":180,"dislike":2,"score":178,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"南方唔卷利嘅國語仲好聽啲。<br />\n北方啲卷撚晒利嘅口吃普通話，真係難聽到嘔。"},{"pid":"94d0e677a17e93e47d0a6b917be4170a3fc339e7","tid":1088440,"uid":15730,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"死北佬"},{"pid":"7f4a28cc0b774668bc210292512914551655e177","tid":1088440,"uid":799,"like":184,"dislike":0,"score":184,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"其實成個南方都比北佬害得好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b8ab3da020b31a7009832e15e08e27804c7dec","tid":1088440,"uid":4574,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"北方溝埋啲垃圾<br />\n胡人雜種 <br />\n講句嘢都有痰"},{"pid":"5a0eb05c294c03da360823914d9300b7a5f00693","tid":1088440,"uid":18484,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"那兒來的屎啊"},{"pid":"9c5cdf6765b79bba790688855b43d7d98bb87e8a","tid":1088440,"uid":239581,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"死支那北佬，切撚咗條脷佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141132efc1594ce2b4365e25a2a3caf6eec569cc","tid":1088440,"uid":18955,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"對於香港人黎講 過左關口以北 都係北方人"},{"pid":"62e45472478e96fd07252110b0ffabe74da80868","tid":1088440,"uid":144372,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"141132efc1594ce2b4365e25a2a3caf6eec569cc","tid":1088440,"uid":18955,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"對於香港人黎講 過左關口以北 都係北方人"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05: